# Project Structure Guide

- This repository is a Dockerized WordPress website using a custom theme `aratavietnam` with TailPress and Vite.
- Primary application code lives in the theme at [themes/aratavietnam](mdc:themes/aratavietnam).
- WordPress + MySQL + WP-CLI are orchestrated via [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml). One-time setup runs in [wp-cli-setup.sh](mdc:wp-cli-setup.sh). Convenience startup script: [start.sh](mdc:start.sh).

## Key Files
- Theme bootstrap: [functions.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/functions.php)
- Main template: [index.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/index.php)
- Header/Footer: [header.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/header.php), [footer.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/footer.php)
- Template parts: [template-parts/content-single.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/template-parts/content-single.php)
- Theme config: [theme.json](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/theme.json)
- PHP classes (PSR-4): [src/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/src) e.g. [src/Pagination.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/src/Pagination.php)
- Frontend entries: [resources/js/app.js](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/js/app.js), [resources/css/app.css](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/app.css)
- Build system: [vite.config.mjs](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/vite.config.mjs), [package.json](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/package.json)
- PHP deps/autoload: [composer.json](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/composer.json)
- Operational docs: [README.md](mdc:README.md)

## High-level Flow
1. Containers start with [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml); WP-CLI provisions WordPress via [wp-cli-setup.sh](mdc:wp-cli-setup.sh) and activates the theme.
2. WordPress loads the active theme; [functions.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/functions.php) initializes TailPress, registers/enqueues assets built by Vite.
3. Requests render via [index.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/index.php) and template parts; custom utilities live in [src/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/src).
